This simple web app generates shuffled partnered-names.

Usage:
1. Type the number of participants and click Submit.
2. Fill-up the empty form of names according to the number of participants you entered.
3. Click Go, and the app will display the names of partners. No duplicates.

Use this on Family/Friends/Company Exchange gifts. Just use codenames to keep it anonymous.

Demo: http://jediscript.com/kriskringler

Pre-requisites:
Download http://twitter.github.io/bootstrap/
